name: Kristina Rose
description:
Tracey Quinn Perez, better known as Kristina Rose, known from classic romantical dramas such as "Deceived", "Bound to Please" and "Scarlet Manor".

This textual inversion model has been trained using Stable Diffusion 1.5 and has been tested on SD1.5-based models. The embed tends to want to draw her with her teeth visible, negative prompts can mitigate this, but it'll likely require a v1.1.

If you enjoy my creations and want to support me or have a face you'd like to commission, consider supporting me on Ko-Fi or Buy Me A Coffee :)
